# =============================================================================
# Three isolated areas (do not mix in git)
#
#  1. PUBLIC WEBSITE     subscriber-site/     → deploy this (GitHub Pages)
#  2. PUBLIC CURRICULUM road-to-machine-learning/ → separate GitHub repo (submodule)
#  3. PRIVATE STUDIO    logo-src/, final-exports/, render_*.js, artboards
#                       → local only, never pushed (ignored below)
#
#  OK on the website: subscriber-site/assets/logo.png (a copy you export manually)
#  NOT on the website: logo-src/, final-exports/, or render tooling
#
#  Do NOT add road-to-machine-learning/ to this file. Submodule = pointer only.
# =============================================================================

# --- Dependencies ---
node_modules/

# --- Secrets ---
.env
.env.*
*.pem

# --- Private channel studio (banners, logos, thumbnails — not the study hub) ---
logo-src/
final-exports/
assets/
artboard.html
artboard-v2.html
facebook-src/
